The gas supply system (black) consists of helium (or nitrogen) and CO2 gas cylinders connected to mass flow controllers (MFC) 1 and 2 respectively, through drying columns (DC) which are packed with zeolite 4A beads and placed in a thermostat set at \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
